OL,5,G1900 Police Interceptors
OL,6,     FJustin and Paul chase down a gang
OL,7,     Fof suspected car thieves. It takes
OL,8,     Fseven interceptors to stop a
OL,9,     Fviolent thief who tries to sink
OL,10,     Fhis teeth into them.
OL,11,G2000 Motorway Cops: Catching Britain's
OL,12,G     Speeders
OL,13,     FPC Tommy Wade is forced to ram a
OL,14,     Fcar to a stop - but why is the
OL,15,     Fdriver so desperate to get away
OL,16,     Ffrom the cops? And police race to
OL,17,     Fa serious two-car collision.
