OL,5,G2100 Police Interceptors
OL,6,     FPolice intercept units on patrol.
OL,7,     FRob and Dan pursue of an
OL,8,     Funder-powered runaway hatchback
OL,9,     Fbefore the suspect decamps and
OL,10,     Fmakes a run for it - in a
OL,11,     Ffluorescent jacket!
OL,12,G2200 Highway Thru Hell
OL,13,     FA semi hits a barrier so hard it
OL,14,     Fblocks the Coq's most important
OL,15,     Fexit, Scott tells Jamie he's fed
OL,16,     Fup with the vintage truck he's
OL,17,     Fdriving, and a new driver shows up
OL,18,     Ffor work.
OL,19,G2300 The X-Files
OL,20,     FA tip from Krycek leads Mulder and
OL,21,     FScully to a meteorite fragment
OL,22,     Fcontaining an alien life form.
