OL,5,G0000 Shoplifters: Caught Red Handed
OL,6,     FThe fight against the rise of
OL,7,     Fshoplifting. In London's West End
OL,8,     Fundercover officers pursue a known
OL,9,     F"dipper", and in Birmingham a
OL,10,     Fstolen bank card scam becomes
OL,11,     Fthreatening. (Ep1)
OL,12,G0100 Outback Truckers
OL,13,     FSteve and dog Bella are in a race
OL,14,     Facross the red deserts of
OL,15,     FAustralia hauling classic cars to
OL,16,     Fauction but delays in loading and
OL,17,     Fthe arrival of the wet season
OL,18,     Fthreaten the journey home.
